          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">Secure and Private System Design for Generative & Agentic AI</p>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">
            July 26, 2026<br>
            9:00 AM (PDT)<br>
            Mtg Room 101A <br>
            Long Beach, <br>
            California, USA
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4">Quick Links</h3>
